definitions.definition: A newb or newbie ; refers to the idea that someone is new to a game, concept, or idea; implying a lack of experience . Also, in some areas the word noob can mean someone is obsessed with things.
examples: Noobs are annoying, they never know the forum rules.

main_definition: ( Internet slang , chiefly derogatory ) A newb or newbie ; refers to the idea that someone is new to a game, concept, or idea; implying a lack of experience . Also, in some areas the word noob can mean someone is obsessed with things.
